<hr>
<h3>Opinionated software</h3>
<p>
  <strong>You introduced the world to the idea of opinionated software 20 years ago</strong>, and I've taken that idea to heart in 
  many of the products I've worked on. Meetle is very opinionated. A few examples: A required purpose statement. 
  One piece of feedback, per page, per attendee rather than lengthy back-and-forths. 
  A small period of time for viewing and feedback.
</p>
